    "start": 138.38,
    "end": 141.07,
    "text": "Yeah? Just start? You can always do a quick [claps].",
    "speaker_id": 0,
    "speaker_name": "Eneasz"
  },
  "38": {
    "start": 141.07,
    "end": 149.52,
    "text": "[laughs] Uh, welcome to Inkhaven Presents: Writers Reading Writing. That's not what it's called.",
    "speaker_id": 1,
    "speaker_name": "Ben"
  },
  "39": {
    "start": 149.52,
    "end": 149.84,
    "text": "[laughs]",
